---

<Layout title="">
  <EventsList
    event_title="Green Colour Day"
    event_sub_title="Explore the latest photos from our Green Colour Day celebration at ISOE"
    paragraph=`Icon School of Excellence celebrated a vibrant
                                Green Colour Day with Nursery and KG students
                                dressed in various shades of green. The day was
                                filled with fun activities, including creative
                                green-themed crafts and interactive storytelling
                                that taught children about nature and the
                                environment. Through games and learning about
                                plants and animals, students enjoyed a day full
                                of laughter, creativity, and community. Thanks
                                to everyone who helped make the event special,
                                and we look forward to more colorful
                                celebrations in the future!`
    images={images}
  />
</Layout>
